						               													<description>Drive fast, grab the garbage and bring it to the landfill!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Wasty &amp;amp; Furious is a quick-to-learn card game for 2 or 3 players. Your goal is to collect as much garbage as you can and bring it to the landfill.&amp;#10;But pay attention! Your opponents want to grab the prize too and will do anything they can to stop you from reaching your intent.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The Gameplay&amp;#10;During set-up each player selects a vehicle data sheet and gets a number of Waste Collect cards depending on its stats (this cards will be visible to all players).&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each player is then given a number of cards depending on the vehicle own Capacity.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;During a game turn, a player can take some actions:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;     play a number of Garbage or Event cards, up to his vehicle Speed&amp;#10;     as soon as he plays an Event card, his turn ends and the cards rules are applied to the following opponent&amp;#10;     instead of playing an Event, he may choose to use a Waste Collect card, that will allow him to collect the garbage on play and refresh his own hand&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;When a player picks up the last card from the deck, the game is going to end. Every player will play a single turn and then all hands will be discarded.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Everyone will then sum up victory points collected during play to see who's the Garbage Man of The Week.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
